---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services | PIVOT Management Consultants" description="Operational intervention — we embed until the numbers move. Operations, Quality & ISO, Innovation, and Change services.">
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-[1.75rem] sm:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.25rem] text-ink mb-2">
        Operational intervention — not training.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-ink-light max-w-2xl">
        Every engagement is measured against your P&L. We embed until the numbers move and your team owns the capability.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Operations</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">Lean line redesign, throughput optimisation, constraint elimination using TRIZ + Six Sigma.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Value stream mapping & redesign</li>
            <li>- Cycle time & throughput improvement</li>
            <li>- TRIZ-based constraint dissolution</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Quality & ISO</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">ISO 9001/13485/AS9100 readiness, CAPA reduction, quality-system architecture.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Quality management system design</li>
            <li>- Audit readiness & gap analysis</li>
            <li>- CAPA process optimisation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Innovation</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">TRIZ-driven product and process innovation. Break contradictions your R&D team has accepted as trade-offs.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Inventive problem-solving workshops</li>
            <li>- Contradiction analysis & resolution</li>
            <li>- Technology roadmap development</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg p-6 bg-surface-alt border border-border">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-ink mb-2">Change & Deployment</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-ink-light mb-3">Baldrige-level CI deployment, leadership alignment, sustainable culture change.</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-ink-muted space-y-1">
            <li>- Enterprise CI programme design</li>
            <li>- Leadership coaching & alignment</li>
            <li>- Capability transfer & sustainability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How we engage -->
  <section class="py-10 sm:py-14 bg-surface-alt border-y border-border">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl mb-5">How we engage</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Diagnostic</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">Start with the Breakthrough Diagnostic to identify where your programme stands and what moves the needle.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Intervention</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">We embed with your team for focused sprints — every session ships measurable results, not just recommendations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-5 border border-border">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-ink mb-1">Transfer</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-ink-light">We build your team's capability so the improvements sustain after we leave. No dependency, no retainers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
